<section class="section wrap" id="services">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="ttl reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span data-ar>خدماتنا</span><span data-en>Our Services</span></span>
      <h2 class="display d-2"><span data-ar>تجربةٌ متكاملة</span><span data-en>A complete experience</span></h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="services">
    <div class="svc-card reveal">
      <div class="svc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M24 4C13 4 4 13 4 24s9 20 20 20 20-9 20-20S35 4 24 4z"/><path d="M24 12v12l8 4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3><span data-ar>توصيل سريع</span><span data-en>Express Delivery</span></h3>
      <p><span data-ar>توصيل في نفس اليوم داخل الرياض، وخلال ٢٤ ساعة لباقي المناطق</span><span data-en>Same-day delivery in Riyadh, 24-hour shipping across the Kingdom</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-card reveal d1">
      <div class="svc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 8h24l4 8H8l4-8z"/><path d="M8 16v24h32V16"/><path d="M20 28h8"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3><span data-ar>تغليف فاخر</span><span data-en>Luxury Packaging</span></h3>
      <p><span data-ar>كل طلب يصلك في صندوق هديّة أنيق، مثاليٌّ للإهداء</span><span data-en>Every order arrives in an elegant gift box, perfect for gifting</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-card reveal d2">
      <div class="svc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M8 24l8 8 24-24"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3><span data-ar>عيّنات الاكتشاف</span><span data-en>Discovery Samples</span></h3>
      <p><span data-ar>جرّب قبل أن تقرر — اطلب عيّنات من مجموعاتنا المختارة</span><span data-en>Try before you decide — order samples from our curated collections</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-card reveal d3">
      <div class="svc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M24 4l4 14h14l-11 8 4 14-11-8-11 8 4-14L7 18h14z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3><span data-ar>استشارة عطرية</span><span data-en>Scent Consultation</span></h3>
      <p><span data-ar>خبراؤنا يساعدونك على اختيار العطر المثاليّ لك ولمن تحب</span><span data-en>Our experts help you find the perfect scent for you and your loved ones</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

